jasima.core.run

类 ExcelExperimentReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.core.run.ExcelExperimentReader

  • public class ExcelExperimentReader
extends java.lang.Object
    Reads and configures an experiment from an Excel-file. This class can also be used to create MultipleConfigurationExperiments or FullFactorialExperiments from such a file.
    版本:
    "$Id$"
    作者:
